{"tid":1806463,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"最新民調：17％香港人支持香港獨立，較上次増加6％","createTime":"2020-01-01T10:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T01:15:40.000Z","uid":282535,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3dffffe43bbc7232ce362def66eba3070cb4bbc3","tid":1806463,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T10:14:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">17%的受訪者表示支持香港脫離中國獨立。</span></span><br />\n41％的受訪者表示，他們&ldquo;強烈反對&rdquo;香港獨立，26％的受訪者表示，&ldquo;有些反對&rdquo;。只有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8％的人表示他們&ldquo;強烈支持&rdquo;獨立性，而9％的人&ldquo;某種程度上支持&rdquo;獨立性。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/amp/5227683.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Famp%2F5227683.html&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIc69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=9dc20683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/amp/5227683.html</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立唯一出路</span></span>"},{"pid":"965c0d9e003bfed47792baa575d4cbc710c0b64c","tid":1806463,"uid":190158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T10:16:17.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"5c7c9ae0ea0fcef806f3834bcd89f5328fdbe852","tid":1806463,"uid":282535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T10:17:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">10月30日</span><br />\n香港民意研究所的民意調查顯示，八成三受訪市民不贊成香港獨立，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">贊成者有11%，5%表示不知或難講</span></span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">贊成港獨的比率，與兩年前由中文大學所作調查相若</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20191030-%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF11%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%B4%8A%E6%88%90%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%9B%A4-%E7%B1%B2%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%8B%BF%E9%80%BC%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8D%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A